    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">If you’d like to try another game, give the <a href="https://emojiscavengerhunt.withgoogle.com/" target="_self">Emoji Scavenger Hunt</a> a whirl — this time, from a browser on your mobile phone.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
