        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">To learn more about TensorFlow.js, visit the project <a href="https://js.tensorflow.org/" target="_self">homepage</a>, check out the <a href="https://js.tensorflow.org/tutorials/" target="_self">tutorials</a>, and try the <a href="https://github.com/tensorflow/tfjs-examples" target="_self">examples</a>. You can also watch the talk from the 2018 TensorFlow Developer Summit, and follow TensorFlow on <a href="http://twitter.com/tensorflow" target="_self">Twitter</a>.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
